#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/06a_Tidings_Good_And_Ill.cfg:256
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hss... Here are the humans who have made a pact with the cursed mermen! "
"Hss..."
msgstr ""
